source.sqlReaderQuery:
select  *  from SIM_103.SIM_BCBS_MI_WEEKLY_DETAILS where Record_Load_Date IN (
    select max(Record_Load_Date) from SIM_103.SIM_BCBS_MI_WEEKLY_DETAILS );

select  *  from SIM_103.SIM_AMBETTER_CED_PATCH_WEEKLY_DETAILS where Record_Load_Date IN (
    select max(Record_Load_Date) from SIM_103.SIM_AMBETTER_CED_PATCH_WEEKLY_DETAILS);

select  *  from SIM_103.SIM_BCBS_TX_POLICY_DETAILS where Record_Load_Date IN (
    select max(Record_Load_Date) from SIM_103.SIM_BCBS_TX_POLICY_DETAILS);

select  *  from SIM_103.SIM_FHCP_WEEKLY_DETAILS where Record_Load_Date IN (
    select max(Record_Load_Date) from SIM_103.SIM_FHCP_WEEKLY_DETAILS);

select  *  from SIM_103.SIM_FHCP_DELINQUENCY_WEEKLY_DETAILS where Record_Load_Date IN (
    select max(Record_Load_Date) from SIM_103.SIM_FHCP_DELINQUENCY_WEEKLY_DETAILS);

select  *  from SIM_103.SIM_AETNA_ACTIVE_POLICY_DETAILS where Record_Load_Date IN (
    select max(Record_Load_Date) from SIM_103.SIM_AETNA_ACTIVE_POLICY_DETAILS );

scriptLines:
query: 'SELECT User_Id, 
       First_Name, 
       Last_Name, 
       Email_Address, 
       Termination_Flag, 
       Department_Name, 
       NPN_Grouping, 
       Upline_Id,
       Upline_First_Name, 
       Upline_Last_Name, 
       Level_Seq, 
       MAX(Record_Load_date) AS Max_Record_Load_date
FROM [AIA_102].[AIA_AGENCY_EMP_HIER_DETAILS_HISTORY] AS emp
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM [AIA_102].[AIA_AGENCY_PAYEE_DETAILS] AS payee
    WHERE payee.Employee_ID = emp.USER_ID
)
GROUP BY User_Id, 
         First_Name, 
         Last_Name, 
         Email_Address, 
         Termination_Flag, 
         Department_Name, 
         NPN_Grouping, 
         Upline_Id,
         Upline_First_Name, 
         Upline_Last_Name, 
         Level_Seq',

query: 'SELECT 
    E2EIS_SEQ_NUMBER,
    CARRIER,
    OWNING_AGENT_OF_RECORD,
    ASSIGNED_AGENT_NUMBER,
    BROKER_START_DATE,
    BROKER_END_DATE,
    PRODUCT_TYPE,
    PRODUCT_DESCRIPTION,
    IMS_TRANSACTION_ID,
    POLICY_STATUS,
    POLICY_ID,
    GROUP_NAME,
    MEMBER_COUNT,
    [ON/OFF_EXCHANGE],
    EXCHANGE_SUBSCRIBER_ID,
    COVERAGE_TYPE,
    SUBSCRIBER_ORIGINAL_EFFECTIVE_DATE,
    COVERAGE_START_DATE,
    COVERAGE_END_DATE,
    PAID_THROUGH_DATE,
    SUBSCRIBER_FIRST_NAME,
    SUBSCRIBER_MIDDLE_NAME,
    SUBSCRIBER_LAST_NAME,
    SUBSCRIBER_FULL_NAME,
    SUBSCRIBER_DOB,
    SUBSCRIBER_EMAIL,
    ADDRESS,
    ADDRESS_2,
    ZIP_CODE,
    CITY,
    STATE,
    COUNTY,
    APP_SUBMIT_DATE,
    MEMBER_PHONE_NUMBER_1,
    MEMBER_PHONE_NUMBER_2,
    COMPENSATION_TYPE,
    COMPENSATION_PERIOD,
    COMPENSATION_AMOUNT,
    PAYEE_NAME,
    MAIN_UPLINE_AGENT,
    GROUP_TEAM_SALES,
    TRANSITION_DATE,
    ASSIGNED_AGENT_NAME,
    AGENCY_ID,
    RECORD_LOAD_DATE,
    RECORD_LOADED_BY,
    RECORD_DATA_SOURCE,
    RECORD_FLAG_STATUS,
    COMMENTS,
    POLICY_ADDED_DATE,
    POLICY_REMOVED_DATE,
    POLICY_CANCELLED_DATE,
    POLICY_REACTIVATION_DATE,
    POLICY_RETENTION_DATE,
    ADDS_MEMBER_COUNT,
    CANCELS_MEMBER_COUNT,
    ORIGINAL_POLICY_STATUS,
    ACTIVITY_FLAG,
    Period_Start_date,
    Period_End_date,
    Period_Name,
    Period_Description,
    Bill_Status,
    AGENCY_SUBSCRIBER_ORIG_EFFDATE,
    AGENCY_SUBSCRIBER_ORIG_EFFDATE_HIS
FROM [AIA_102].[AIA_BOOK_OF_BUSSINESS_ALL_CARRIERS_JOINED]
ORDER BY 
    CARRIER ASC,
    POLICY_ID ASC,
    POLICY_STATUS ASC,
    COVERAGE_START_DATE DESC;',

query: 'Select 

CONTRACT_YEAR,EMPLOYEE_TYPE,EMPLOYEE_ID,FULL_NAME,PRIMARY_ROLE,MONTHLY_RENEWAL_WRITING_AGENT_COMP_TIER,

PRE_ACA_WRITING_AGENT_COMP_TIER,LTL_WRITING_AGENT_COMP_TIER,MED_SUP_WRITING_AGENT_COMP_TIER,

DENTAL_NEWSALE_WRITING_AGENT_COMP_TIER,ACA_NEWSALE_WRITING_AGENT_COMP_TIER,GROUP_WRITING_AGENT_COMP_TIER,

MAIN_UPLINE_FULL_NAME,ROLE_END_DATE,ROLE_END_REASON,ALL_SALES_PAYEE,SUBMITTING_AGENT,SECONDARY_ROLE,

DEPARTMENT_ENTITY_ID,DEPARTMENT_NAME,[HEALTH_ACA_EMPLOYEE TIER],ADVANCE_OVERRIDE_PAYEE_ID

DENTAL_NEWSALE_WRITING_AGENT_COMP_TIER,ACA_NEWSALE_WRITING_AGENT_COMP_TIER,GROUP_WRITING_AGENT_COMP_TIER,

ANCILLARY_RENEWAL_WRITING_AGENT_COMP_TIER,PAYROLL_ID,PAYEE_EMPLOYEE_ID,PAYEE_NAME,MAIN_UPLINE_EMPLOYEE_ID,

MAIN_UPLINE_FULL_NAME,ROLE_END_DATE,ROLE_END_REASON,ALL_SALES_PAYEE,SUBMITTING_AGENT,SECONDARY_ROLE,

DEPARTMENT_ENTITY_ID,DEPARTMENT_NAME,[HEALTH_ACA_EMPLOYEE TIER],ADVANCE_OVERRIDE_PAYEE_ID

from [AIA_102].AIA_AGENCY_PAYEE_DETAILS_AUTOMATION_TO_LOAD',
